    <entry>
      <title>智能指针 2025/8/30</title>
      <link href="/2026/03/26/%E6%99%BA%E8%83%BD%E6%8C%87%E9%92%88-2025-8-30/"/>
      <url>/2026/03/26/%E6%99%BA%E8%83%BD%E6%8C%87%E9%92%88-2025-8-30/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>也是之前一段时间准备面试的时候写的，现在记录保存</p><p>理解上是定义一个类，然后这个类的析构函数会自动删除生成的指针，类内成员包括这个指针(私有)。</p><p>共享智能指针(shared_ptr)</p><p>使用方法</p><figure class="highlight c++"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="function">shared_ptr&lt;<span class="type">int</span>&gt; <span class="title">age</span><span class="params">(<span class="keyword">new</span> <span class="type">int</span>(<span class="number">88</span>))</span></span>;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">//更推荐的写法</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">//shared_ptr&lt;int&gt; age = make_shared&lt;int&gt;(88);</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">//它更高效，因为它只需要一次内存分配，而 new 和 shared_ptr 的构造函数需要两次（一次为对象，一次为控制块）</span></span><br><span class="line">cout &lt;&lt; *age &lt;&lt; endl;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>智能指针和原生指针(裸指针)不能相互转换</p><p>如</p><figure class="highlight c++"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="type">int</span>* temp = age;<span class="comment">//false</span></span><br><span class="line">shared_ptr&lt;<span class="type">int</span>&gt; temp = age; <span class="comment">//right</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>接着上面的情况，假设代码如下</p><figure class="highlight c++"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="function">shared_ptr&lt;<span class="type">int</span>&gt; <span class="title">age</span><span class="params">(<span class="keyword">new</span> <span class="type">int</span>(<span class="number">88</span>))</span></span>;</span><br><span class="line">&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    shared_ptr&lt;<span class="type">int</span>&gt; temp = age; <span class="comment">//退出去后就会析构，超出作用域</span></span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>那么age是否还能访问，答案是可以的，因为有中间层</p><p><img src="C:\Users\littlec\AppData\Roaming\Typora\typora-user-images\中间层.png" alt="image-20250830101741800"></p><p>只有引用计数到0的时候才彻底释放对应的内存</p><figure class="highlight c++"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">age.<span class="built_in">reset</span>();<span class="comment">//reset 没有参数版本，就是放弃自己的所有权，引用计数-1，如果此时引用计数减为0，那么就会释放指向的对象</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>一旦使用智能指针，就不再推荐使用裸指针了</p><p>如果确实需要裸指针，可以通过 get() 方法获取，但要非常小心其生命周期。</p><figure class="highlight c++"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">cout &lt;&lt; age.<span class="built_in">use_count</span>()  &lt;&lt; endl <span class="comment">//得到引用计数</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">if</span> (age.<span class="built_in">unique</span>())</span><br><span class="line">&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    cout &lt;&lt; <span class="string">&quot;只有你指向该对象&quot;</span> &lt;&lt; endl;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">else</span></span><br><span class="line">&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    cout &lt;&lt; <span class="string">&quot;不只有你指向该对象，引用计数大于1&quot;</span> &lt;&lt; endl;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>独占指针 同时只能有一个指针指向该对象，不能赋值，只能移动</p><figure class="highlight c++"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="function">unique_ptr&lt;string&gt; <span class="title">up</span><span class="params">(<span class="keyword">new</span> string(<span class="string">&quot;test&quot;</span>))</span></span>;</span><br><span class="line">cout &lt;&lt; *up &lt;&lt; endl;</span><br><span class="line">cout &lt;&lt; up-&gt;<span class="built_in">size</span>() &lt;&lt; endl;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">//独占，没有引用计数，不可以如下操作</span></span><br><span class="line">unique_ptr&lt;string&gt; s1 = up; <span class="comment">//拷贝构造函数已删除</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">//</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function">unique_ptr&lt;string&gt; <span class="title">get_ptr</span><span class="params">(<span class="type">const</span> <span class="type">char</span>* s)</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"></span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="built_in">unique_ptr</span>&lt;string&gt;(<span class="keyword">new</span> <span class="built_in">string</span>(s));</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">unique_ptr&lt;string&gt; s2 = <span class="built_in">get_ptr</span>(<span class="string">&quot;hello world&quot;</span>);<span class="comment">//可行</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">//get_ptr 返回的是一个右值 unique_ptr，发生了移动语义（move semantics）。unique_ptr 支持移动构造和移动赋值，这使得所有权的转移成为可能，而不是拷贝。</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight c++"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">cout &lt;&lt; *s<span class="number">2.</span><span class="built_in">release</span>() &lt;&lt; endl;<span class="comment">//返回对象的裸指针，把自己的所有权交出，注意内存并没有释放</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>plus</p><p>weak_ptr 是 shared_ptr 的一个补充。它不拥有对象的所有权，因此不会增加引用计数。它主要用于解决 shared_ptr 导致的循环引用问题。</p><figure class="highlight c++"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">class</span> <span class="title class_">B</span>; <span class="comment">// 前向声明</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">class</span> <span class="title class_">A</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">public</span>:</span><br><span class="line">    shared_ptr&lt;B&gt; b_ptr;</span><br><span class="line">    ~<span class="built_in">A</span>() &#123; cout &lt;&lt; <span class="string">&quot;A destroyed&quot;</span> &lt;&lt; endl; &#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">class</span> <span class="title class_">B</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">public</span>:</span><br><span class="line">    shared_ptr&lt;A&gt; a_ptr; <span class="comment">// 如果这里是 shared_ptr，则会造成循环引用</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">// weak_ptr&lt;A&gt; a_ptr; // 使用 weak_ptr 解决循环引用</span></span><br><span class="line">    ~<span class="built_in">B</span>() &#123; cout &lt;&lt; <span class="string">&quot;B destroyed&quot;</span> &lt;&lt; endl; &#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>当 A 和 B 互相持有对方的 shared_ptr 时，它们的引用计数永远不会降到零，导致内存泄漏。使用 weak_ptr 可以在不形成循环引用的情况下访问对象。</p><p><strong>自定义删除器 (Deleter):</strong><br>unique_ptr 和 shared_ptr 都支持自定义删除器。这意味着你可以指定一个函数或函数对象来替代默认的 delete 操作。这在管理非堆内存资源（如文件句柄、数据库连接）时非常有用。</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">// unique_ptr 自定义删除器</span><br><span class="line">auto file_closer = [](FILE* fp) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    if (fp) fclose(fp);</span><br><span class="line">&#125;;</span><br><span class="line">unique_ptr&lt;FILE, decltype(file_closer)&gt; fp(fopen(&quot;test.txt&quot;, &quot;r&quot;), file_closer);</span><br><span class="line">// shared_ptr 自定义删除器</span><br><span class="line">shared_ptr&lt;int&gt; array_ptr(new int[10], [](int* p) &#123; delete[] p; &#125;);</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><strong>何时选择哪种智能指针:</strong></p><ul><li><strong>unique_ptr</strong>: 当你希望某个对象具有唯一所有权时，优先选择 unique_ptr。它开销最小，且强制执行独占语义。</li><li><strong>shared_ptr</strong>: 当多个智能指针需要共享同一个对象的所有权，并且需要在最后一个所有者销毁时才释放对象时，选择 shared_ptr。</li><li><strong>weak_ptr</strong>: 当你需要观察一个 shared_ptr 管理的对象，但又不想增加其引用计数，尤其是在处理循环引用时，选择 weak_ptr。</li></ul>]]></content>
      
      
      
